{
  "stem": "13673.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the kids were like from very, very young, three, four years old, to-- the cut-off age was 17.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it was all a mixture of kids.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of course, we all had to-- wanted to be by the window, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I know I, I was able to wave good-bye to my father in Stuttgart.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They said they would come to England in about six weeks after, and I believed them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think not too many, except for the German officers that were on the train with us, you know, they were the SS people.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To keep us in line or to make sure that we were going where we were going, and-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have-- I don't remember anything bad happening on my particular train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I've heard other children who had come out on other Kindertransports, where these SS people were really nasty and opened up their suitcases and just threw everything around and really mean.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I honestly don't remember anything like that happening.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, then my-- this was the town that my mother was born in and where my grandmother still lived, and she came to the train station to say good-bye to me.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Again, I don't think I understood the, the gravity of it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think I understood that perhaps this would be the last time we would see each other.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And indeed, it was the last time I would see my grandmother because later she was killed in Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But she brought me a little present.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It, it isn't the original, but it was exactly like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where should I hold it, like that?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- it's-- actually, there were two books.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
